Enum Class HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping>
org.graalvm.polyglot.HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping>, Constable
Enclosing class:
HostAccess
public static enum HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping extends Enum<HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping>
List of default host object mappings of mutable target types available in Value.as(Class). The mappings map guest object traits to host object types.
Since:
23.0
